Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.56,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}反射般的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:33.90,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我作出让自己心痛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:43.16,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\cH0\4cHFFFFFF}暧昧的线在摇荡的缝隙间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:50.63,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\cH0\4cHFFFFFF}我用天真的小聪明延续着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:57.47,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\cH0\4cHFFFFFF}尽是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:01.14,IN-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\cH0\4cHFFFFFF}尽是伤痕
